[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0839","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1002","title":"Netscape Navigator 邮件密码弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Netscape Navigator 浏览器在存储用户邮件密码时采用弱加密算法，导致本地攻击者能够通过分析加密数据恢复明文密码。该漏洞存在于密码存储机制中，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用弱加密算法的可逆特性即可获取用户凭证信息，可能导致邮箱账户被非法访问。受影响版本包括 Netscape Navigator 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1002"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.997","remediation":"立即停止使用 Netscape Navigator 内置邮件客户端收发邮件，迁移至 Mozilla Firefox、Google Chrome 等现代浏览器或 Thunderbird 等独立邮件客户端访问邮件服务。如暂无法迁移，在 Netscape 首选项中关闭密码记忆功能，每次手动输入邮箱密码，避免凭据持久化存储于本地弱加密文件中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94536309217214&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94570673523998&w=2","http://www.rstcorp.com/news/bad-crypto.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1002","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1002.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723/GHSA-wf2x-w2q8-7723.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1002.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152000_152100.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d48d045b-59cc-4474-90a9-e6ede9ca2247.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0839.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1198","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0894","title":"Red Hat Linux screen 程序本地终端写入漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 的 screen 终端复用程序未使用 Unix98 伪终端（ptys），导致其创建的终端会话缺乏必要的权限隔离机制。本地攻击者可通过向其他用户使用的 screen 终端写入数据，实现会话劫持或任意命令注入。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 多个版本，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地系统账户，攻击复杂度低，危害等级为高危。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0894"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.680","remediation":"升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.2 及以上版本（默认启用 Unix98 ptys），或单独升级 screen 程序至 3.07.06 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 screen 配置文件中添加 `defunix98 on` 启用 Unix98 pty 支持，并限制本地非信任用户登录系统以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0894"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1198.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1106","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0876","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 在处理 EMBED 标签时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造包含超长 EMBED 标签属性的恶意 HTML 页面，当用户使用 IE 4.0 访问该页面时触发缓冲区溢出，导致攻击者可在当前用户上下文中执行任意代码，完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上使用 IE 4.0 的所有版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0876"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.490","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 4.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本，该版本修复了 EMBED 标签解析时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于当前仍在使用旧版 IE 的环境，建议升级至受支持的现代浏览器（如 Microsoft Edge），并禁用已停止维护的 IE 浏览器中 ActiveX 及 EMBED 标签的调用权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ185959","http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q176/6/97.asp"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1106.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0350","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0735","title":"KDE K-Mail 符号链接攻击本地权限提升漏洞","description":"KDE K-Mail 在处理临时用户目录时存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意的符号链接，诱导 K-Mail 以高权限向攻击者控制的位置写入文件，从而实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.1/1.1.2、Caldera kdenetwork 1.1.1-1、Caldera OpenLinux 1.3/2.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0735"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.883","remediation":"升级 KDE 至 2.0 及以上版本（该版本重构了临时文件处理机制，采用 mkstemp 代替可预测路径）；对应发行版适用：RedHat Linux 升级至 6.0 以上 errata 内核/kdebase 包，Caldera OpenLinux 升级至 2.3 以上。临时缓解措施：为邮件用户设置私有临时目录环境变量（如 TMPDIR=/tmp/kmail-$USER）并限制目录权限为 0700。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999015_01.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/300","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19240"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0350.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0756","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0756.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0964","title":"FreeBSD libc setlocale 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD libc 模块中的 setlocale 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置超长 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，成功利用后可获得目标系统的 root 权限或劫持进程控制流。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0964"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.217","remediation":"升级至 FreeBSD 4.0 及以上版本（该版本已修复 libc 中 PATH_LOCALE 长度检查缺失问题）；现代系统应升级至最新的受支持 FreeBSD 稳定版（如 13.x 或 14.x）。如无法升级，可通过在系统级脚本中过滤并截断 PATH_LOCALE 环境变量长度（限制 ≤256 字节）作为临缓解措施，并严格限制本地 shell 访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0756.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1900","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1324","title":"OpenVMS VAXstations 登录失败锁定机制绕过漏洞","description":"Open VMS VAXstations 5.3 至 5.5-2 版本中，当使用 VMS DECwindows 或 MOTIF 图形界面时，系统未能正确限制超过登录失败阈值的用户账户访问权限。具体而言，当用户账户因多次登录失败触发 break-in 限制后，系统并未实际禁用该账户，导致攻击者可以绕过账户锁定机制持续进行暴力破解密码攻击。该漏洞降低了暴力破解的难度，使远程攻击者更容易通过枚举方式获取系统访问权限，影响所有运行受影响版本 Open VMS 的 VAXstations 设备。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1324"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:11.863","remediation":"升级 Open VMS 至 5.5-3 或更高版本，该版本已修复登录失败阈值检测失效问题。如无法升级，在 SYLOGIN.COM 或系统登录脚本中增加登录失败计数检查逻辑，并启用 SYSGEN 参数 LGI_BRK_LIM 强制限制。同时配置 INTRUSION_RECORD 启用入侵检测记录，监控异常登录行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-06.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7225","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1324","https://github.com/bb1nfosec/Information-Security-Tasks/blob/14e2094f7bd96d2cb82493a9a6968ae7aa4fed5e/feeds/2026-06-07.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1324.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1324.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp/GHSA-5r36-3w36-p2fp.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_200_300.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87872/info.html","https://github.com/jmohitz/SECAI/blob/33119e592f944e313664a5f75ae76284ea4b3fe8/data/CWE/307.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1900.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1293","title":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 mod_proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及更早版本中的 mod_proxy 模块存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的畸形 FTP 命令，触发 mod_proxy 模块在处理 FTP 代理请求时出现错误，导致 Apache 进程崩溃转储核心。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响运行 Apache 1.2.5 及之前版本的系统，攻击者可通过持续发送恶意请求造成服务不可用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1293"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:07.733","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.3.x 或更高版本（1.2.5 及更早版本已停止维护）。如无法升级，在配置中禁用 mod_proxy 模块或限制代理请求来源 IP。同时建议迁移至当前主流版本（2.4.x）以获得持续安全支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88413292830649&w=2","http://www.apache.org/info/security_bulletin_1.2.5.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1293","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json","https://github.com/zmerry/z-marvel.github.io/blob/581a79f0e7ceb8cdb3e444922154e004cca44bbb/vulbox/webvul/high/Apache%E7%9A%84mod_proxy%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E(CVE-1999-1293).html","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1293.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-1293.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1809","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1246","title":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Direct Mailer 明文密码存储漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 3.0 的 Direct Mailer 功能将用户域名和密码以明文形式保存在 TMLBQueue 网络共享中，该共享目录默认权限设置不当，允许网络中的任意用户访问。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络共享读取存储的凭据信息，进而获取系统权限。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 3.0 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1246"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.790","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft KB Q229972 安全更新以解决 Direct Mailer 明文存储密码问题。如无法安装更新，手动收紧 TMLBQueue 网络共享的 NTFS 权限，仅允许授权管理员账户访问，移除 Everyone/Anonymous 写入权限，并启用 SMB 签名防止中间人窃取。建议尽快迁移至受支持的邮件服务产品，Site Server 3.0 已停止技术支持，无法获得后续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q229/9/72.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2068","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1246","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1246.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-99cm-v3cq-wf9j/GHSA-99cm-v3cq-wf9j.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1246.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87849/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--bcb834d4-2dd0-4c27-9456-4d8219890aab.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1809.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1800","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1233","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 域名解析访问限制漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 存在访问限制绕过漏洞。当用户发起初始会话请求且其 IP 地址无法反向解析为 DNS 域名时，IIS 未能正确限制该请求的访问权限，即所谓的\"域名解析\"漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过使用无法解析到 DNS 域名的 IP 地址发起初始会话请求，绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1233"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.120","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-039 提供的 IIS 4.0 域限制热修复补丁（KB241562/KB241805），该补丁修正了 IIS 4.0 在 IP 地址无法解析为 DNS 域名时错误放行首次会话请求的问题。由于 IIS 4.0 及 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）并部署最新版 IIS。临时缓解措施：在 IIS 管理器中禁用基于域名的访问限制策略，改为使用 IP 地址范围限制；同时确保反向 DNS 解析服务正常工作，避免因解析失败导致访问绕过。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q241/5/62.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/657","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-039","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1233","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1233.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh/GHSA-53c2-2qjx-38qh.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1233.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1233.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--f8160a66-e7e6-44ab-9c71-410f00677cdc.json","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1800.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1709","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1709.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1127","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 命名管道 RPC 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的命名管道 RPC 连接关闭机制存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含畸形数据的连接请求，导致系统无法正常关闭无效的命名管道 RPC 连接，从而引发资源耗尽型拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。微软已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1127"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.667","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-017 提供的补丁程序（KB195733）。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2012 或更高版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面阻止对 RPC 服务（TCP/UDP 135 端口）的匿名外部访问，并限制命名管道连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/Q195/7/33.asp","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/523.php","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-017","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1127","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1127.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1127.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2/GHSA-fjjp-8g8w-55f2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86274/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_