hub.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288/GHSA-wcrg-6ghq-6288.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88085/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1094.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000992.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1087","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 无点IP地址安全区域绕过漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4 在处理 URL 中的 32 位无点 IP 地址时存在解析逻辑缺陷，将点分十进制格式以外的纯数字 IP 地址误识别为主机名而非 IP 地址，导致浏览器错误地应用本地 Intranet 区域安全策略。远程攻击者可构造包含无点 IP 地址的恶意 URL，诱使用户访问后绕过正常的安全区隔离，从而执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 4 及早期版本，增大了内网环境下的攻击面。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.647","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.0 或更高版本，或改用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。IE 4 已停止支持且不再接收安全更新，应彻底停止使用。无法升级时可配置代理服务器过滤包含纯数字 IP 的 URL 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q168/6/17.asp","http://www.microsoft.com/Windows/Ie/security/dotless.asp","http://www.osvdb.org/7828","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-016","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2209","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1087","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1087.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c/GHSA-9rv3-rxw8-xr7c.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000990.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1087.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99ba35f8-d4eb-4aae-be83-0d60e01586a1.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1687","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1055","title":"Microsoft Excel 97 工作表函数任意代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Excel 97 在调用工作表函数前未向用户发出安全警告，攻击者可通过构造包含恶意 CALL 函数的 XLS 文件诱导用户打开，利用 CALL 函数加载并执行恶意 DLL，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Excel 97 及后续兼容版本，攻击者可通过社会工程方式诱导受害者打开特制文档触发，无需身份认证。目前已存在公开利用代码，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1055"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.767","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-018 提供的补丁程序，该补丁可通过 https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018 获取。同时在 Excel 中将宏安全级别设置为\"高\"以阻止未签名的 CALL 函数执行，并建议升级到 Office 2000 及以上版本以彻底规避该问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/179","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-018","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1737","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1055","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1055.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1055.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97/GHSA-cx75-p9pm-2q97.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_600_700.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-356.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1055.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1687.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1051","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1335","title":"Red Hat Linux cmu-snmp snmpd 配置错误漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 4.0 系统中 cmu-snmp 软件包 3.3-1 之前版本的 snmpd 服务器存在配置错误漏洞。由于默认配置不当，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统上的敏感信息进行读取或写入操作，导致信息泄露或系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 4.0 及使用相关 cmu-snmp 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1335"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.290","remediation":"升级 cmu-snmp 软件包至 3.3-1 或更高版本，并修改 SNMP 配置文件 /etc/snmp/snmpd.conf，将默认 public/private 团体字改为复杂随机字符串；同时在 iptables 防火墙中限制仅信任 IP 可访问 UDP 161 端口，禁用 SNMP 写权限（read-only）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh40-errata-general.html#cmu-snmp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7251","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1335","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1335.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x/GHSA-pr33-x2p7-6w2x.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1335.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153900_154000.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001032.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--54c919b9-3bdc-4906-ba93-56a73c55a239.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1051.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1050","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1334","title":"Elm 2.4 filter 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Elm 2.4 邮件客户端的 filter 命令存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向受害者发送包含超长 From: 或 Reply-To: 头的恶意邮件，或诱使用户以超长 -f 参数运行 filter 命令，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Elm 2.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1334"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:13.147","remediation":"升级 Elm 到 2.4.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令中的缓冲区溢出问题。Red Hat 在 RH50 errata 中发布了针对 elm 的安全更新。如无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或避免使用 Elm 处理不可信来源的邮件，同时可考虑迁移至现代邮件客户端如 Thunderbird 或 Mutt。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88609666024181&w=2","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#elm","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1334","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1334.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1334.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm/GHSA-9pwm-wh34-fpxm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999